dct_title_s: Chart of the Delaware River along the Camden Waterfront from Newton Creek to Cooper Point III
dct_description_sm: Camden along the Delaware River from Newton Creek to Cooper Creek. Map shows the 6, 12, 18, 24,30, 35 foot curves of depth, pierhead and bulkhead lines, the location of stations and monuments and a table with listings of course, bearing, and distances.
